skins.name: Default
skins.secIdle1Text: Commander, it's so warm here! I think I can relax like this...
skins.secIdle2Text: Thatcher's over there! She's making me anxious~!
skins.secIdle3Text: Ausburne isn't like Thatcher at all... She actually helps me when I need it!
skins.secTouchText: I'm sorry that I don't live up to your expectations, Commander...
skins.secSpecialTouchText: Eeek~! Um... W-what am I supposed to...
